        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Google doesn’t like to see the same content repeated in multiple places. Make sure each individual content appears only once on your site - link to it from elsewhere if need be. Alternatively, you can use ",
