        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "heading",
        "tag": "h2",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Content that sits on its own within a site can easily end up down-rated by search engines against your general site ranking. Make sure you have good site linking structure, so that every piece of content is linked by several other pieces of content.",
